item.title: People of ProsperUS: Simmons Family
item.description: People of ProsperUS: The Simmons Family By: Weyman Cohen Tag Team Autoworks is a collision shop specializing in detailing. Tag Team Autoworks (TTA) has an office that does government contracts. There is a division of the business that goes into housing and urban development. **The Simmons family mission **is to get the collision shop up and running. Gerald, having suffered dozens of heart attacks, serves his family as a teacher of business.
